Data

  • evals: Course evaluations dataset
  • kissing: Kissing side dataset

  • NBA1011: Data from 2010-2011 NBA season (Data Expeditions)
  • paris_paintings: Data from paintings sold at auctions in Paris in the 18th century (Data Expeditions)
